PROJECT.NAME: icAstAngu
PROJECT.TITLE: Astagobius angustatus
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project collects the sequencing data and draft assemblies generated for Astagobius angustatus by the European Reference Genome Atlas (ERGA, https://www.erga-biodiversity.eu/) for the Biodiversity Genomics Europe project (BGE, https://biodiversitygenomics.eu/).
